CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 10, 1959, pg. 14, reads: "Senior Matron Honored - Mrs. Annie Williams, seated third from left, Grand Senior Matron of the State of Pennsylvania, was honored with a testimonial reception recently at the Masonic Temple, which was sponsored by Mary Ella Court, No. 6, Heroines of Jericho... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Three men and eight women gathered for reception honoring Grand Senior Matron Williams in Masonic Temple
